      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 64,
      "message": "The USE_HTTPS name was proposed by https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/TLS+support+for+CBS+-+Migration+Plan\n\n\"CBS Enhancement  (DCAEGEN2-1549)\n\n    Support HTTPS enablement via environment variable\n        USE_HTTPS: set to “1” to use HTTPS, anything else is HTTP\n        HTTPS_KEY_PATH: path to the TLS private key\n        HTTPS_CERT_PATH: path to the TLS certificate\n    Use port 10443 if USE_HTTPS is set to “1”, otherwise  port 10000\"\n\nSo I'm not quite sure if I can rename it.",
